{"tid":2295980,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"何小鵬反擊 Elon Musk 抄襲指控  稱將於中國汽車市場擊敗 Tesla","createTime":"2020-11-22T06:32:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-22T17:24:24.000Z","uid":105678,"like":21,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"8075d7ef80ff14a0e9cd5ac8d223dcd1f752d793","tid":2295980,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T06:32:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/648.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2F648.jpg&h=83a28a22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國電動車新創公司小鵬汽車日前表示將會從 2021 年起生產的車型採用激光雷達技術以升級自動駕駛軟件系統，惹來 Tesla 創辦人 Elon Musk 於社交媒體 Twitter 上轉載相關消息，並諷刺對方抄襲 Tesla。而在今日，小鵬汽車 CEO 何小鵬就於微信上反擊 Elon Musk 的言論，並表示將於中國擊敗對方。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/news-16059277863039.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2Fnews-16059277863039.jpg&h=d92d6e6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n小鵬汽車 CEO 何小鵬在今日於微信的朋友圈上發表一則貼文，當中表示公司最新發布所配備激光雷達的小鵬下一代自動駕駛架構令位於世界西邊的某一人 (Elon Musk) 感到不滿，以回應對方早前指控自己抄襲的言論，重申造謠已經被證明是無法打敗任何競爭對手。<br />\n<br />\n何小鵬又在該貼文中疑似挑釁 Elon Musk，指出對方如果從明年開始於中國採用自動駕駛技術的時候需準備被小鵬汽車的最新技術震驚，並表示雙方終有一天將於國際的汽車市場上相遇。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：East money"},{"pid":"0e600c870dc241304ab8c831df4b5fa98f62e867","tid":2295980,"uid":231583,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T06:33:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d181d0e63f3f3a4ff2ef079cc7ecc21691752613","tid":2295980,"uid":104138,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T06:36:17.000Z","msg":"傻閪musk"},{"pid":"660ab26502e8a9abf3e1363c70fc31bb84b4ff2a","tid":2295980,"uid":104447,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T06:36:56.000Z","msg":"可以成為國企了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f99a711e86a0bbbc1e8be41906179add74e1dc7b","tid":2295980,"uid":103230,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T06:38:34.000Z","msg":"transmission completed"},{"pid":"3a21ec91a2f9d29b8c12033ccd212150a3d7efcb","tid":2295980,"uid":271397,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T06:42:12.000Z","msg":"中文都寫唔掂, 正廢柴<br />\n<br />\n個「你」字後面無啦啦跟乜鳩頓號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"116f8ab94cb54868c2fd7801c28910b8bd0e1c4a","tid":2295980,"uid":282637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T06:47:58.000Z","msg":"有中國特色社會主義,班白皮豬識條鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f16d56ac739f1c4ac607e6e4d8eae1b91a5c8ae9","tid":2295980,"uid":56819,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T06:48:33.000Z","msg":"支持踢Tesla出支那市場,等佢仲奶得咁過癮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"810ed9c3f4989431c3bad7d55b22a0cb8492e124","tid":2295980,"uid":14449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T06:50:54.000Z","msg":"人地支火箭可以打直落番地面<br />\n你點樣過呀？"},{"pid":"82ca48c93a6047c7704f1ad0154f06e40d79a22b","tid":2295980,"uid":39365,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T06:52:41.000Z","msg":"因果報應呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22cc8343d6dabc44c0db79487d2b57e7439c027c","tid":2295980,"uid":2429,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T06:53:17.000Z","msg":"股價升就ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf13c6aa701281bd0452af1c39b343011549dbf1","tid":2295980,"uid":76261,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T06:56:16.000Z","msg":"Musk係中國開廠應該係人生最on9既決定"},{"pid":"23b1ff427227f0076bcdd65b328b9b5c8d82e89d","tid":2295980,"uid":11001,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T06:58:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>指出對方如果從明年開始於中國採用自動駕駛技術的時候需準備被小鵬汽車的最新技術震驚</blockquote><br />\n自炒技術 <img src